        <title>Can&#39;t use Gparted in symaint?</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[arraybolt3]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Try using:</p>
<pre><code class="lang-auto">gsudo-x gparted
</code></pre>
<p>(<code>gsudo-x</code> is a sudo wrapper in Kicksecure that does the needed workarounds to allow XWayland access to apps running as root.)</p>
